        {
            "title": "NBA｜當積首作客倒戈達拉斯 感觸含淚轟45分 助湖人贏波奪季後賽資格(有片)",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"當積強忍淚水。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/859699f77d94c5f7376f7d3029bdd1cc/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250410/_2025041013455810908.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">當積強忍淚水。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周三NBA焦點之戰，當積(Luka Doncic)自被交易後首次作客重返達拉斯倒戈獨行俠，會方賽前播致敬影片時，當積幾乎感動得流淚。但他未受情緒影響，轟入45分助湖人以112:97取勝，同時鎖定季後賽席位。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積強忍淚水。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e406753d0461dbcc1fc1c78a51c78be8/2025-04/2025-04-10T000332Z_1598591610_MT1USATODAY25888884_RTRMADP_3_NBA-LOS-ANGELES-LAKERS-AT-DALLAS-MAVERICKS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積強忍淚水。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積強忍淚水。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b581dafd958c1a0987314ce726ab89ab/2025-04/Lakers_Mavericks_Basketball_07531--7f7fd.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積強忍淚水。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積強忍淚水。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0d542d7a23799e283648af1d9338080f/2025-04/Lakers_Mavericks_Basketball_09312--be8d8.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積強忍淚水。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積十分感動。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f8af15f143355a8a0c10647bf1c657fd/2025-04/Lakers_Mavericks_Basketball_15840--3a333.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積十分感動。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積轟入45分。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/915cefcd3c9f9789177c22d073286e76/2025-04/Lakers_Mavericks_Basketball_94008--ee724.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積轟入45分。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積轟入45分。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0f7e807f4b318b508535ee9ae6ff5ea7/2025-04/Lakers_Mavericks_Basketball_40434--617d3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積轟入45分。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積轟入45分。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/82f3f6956b049c08c90f716a9be88aea/2025-04/Lakers_Mavericks_Basketball_80344--33d60.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積轟入45分。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積轟入45分。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/49a36485a6c64e1cdeeccb168654156b/2025-04/Lakers_Mavericks_Basketball_70292--f5d2b.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積轟入45分。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"當積轟入45分。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8e48db8f0730f7f9718a7c851617bb2c/2025-04/Lakers_Mavericks_Basketball_97616--68745.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        當積轟入45分。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"達拉斯球迷十分支持當積。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d59d9b64335b97cdd7ff546d8e48fdbb/2025-04/Lakers_Mavericks_Basketball_20260--b35ab.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        達拉斯球迷十分支持當積。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>當積首倒戈強忍淚水</h2>\n<p>當積於2月突被獨行俠交易至湖人震驚球壇，今仗是他被交易後首次造訪達拉斯倒戈舊主。賽前介紹球員時，會方特別播出致敬影片，回顧他在球隊的6年生涯，獲全場球迷歡呼拍掌。如此場面令當積十分感動，在場邊明顯眼泛淚光，更要用毛巾抹眼淚。\n\n</p><h2>相關片段：</h2>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\" xml:lang=\"en\">The Mavs introduce an emotional Luka Doncic 🥹 <a href=\"https://t.co/ElpyWfMy1a\">pic.twitter.com/ElpyWfMy1a</a>\n— BricksCenter (@BricksCenter) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BricksCenter/status/1910115824003923976?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">April 9, 2025</a></p></blockquote>\n<script async=\"\" charset=\"utf-8\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\"></script>\n<h2>轟45分助湖人鎖定季後賽席位</h2>\n<p>雖然百感交集，但當積仍打出高水平表現，貢獻45分和8個籃板，助湖人以112:97奏捷。至於首倒戈湖人的安東尼戴維斯則只入13分。當積賽後直言：「我自己都不知道是怎麼做到，當我在看致敬視頻時，我以為自己肯定不能專注比賽，但所有隊友都全力支持我。非常感激達拉斯球迷，我愛他們，也愛這座城市，但現在是時候向前看了。」另外，戰罷今場後，湖人以49勝31負排西岸第3位，落實直接取得季後賽資格。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
