        {
            "title": "拼多多熱銷「對等關稅戰參戰」紀念杯 網民：見證歷史",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"拼多多熱銷「對等關稅戰參戰」紀念杯。拼多多截圖\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/0c23d3c9134f7e9081ea54b9bd3f6079/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250410/_2025041013344498531.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">拼多多熱銷「對等關稅戰參戰」紀念杯。拼多多截圖</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>中美關稅博弈愈演愈烈之際，內地電商平台淘寶和拼多多近日湧現了多款「對等關稅戰參戰」紀念杯，引網民驚歎商家「結合時事、創意無限」，大呼「見證歷史」「也算是參戰了」。\n\n</p>\n<p>《星島》記者搜索發現，淘寶和拼多多有大量商家銷售印有上述字樣的中國老式搪瓷杯，售價多在10至26元人民幣之間。拼多多界面顯示，前來拼單的顧客絡繹不絕，可見產品頗受歡迎。此外，抖音平台亦有大量相關內容。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3445487/\">中對美84%關稅生效｜海關總署：「在運貨物」暫免徵 特殊緩衝期33天</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"淘寶熱銷「對等關稅戰參戰」紀念杯。淘寶截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eebb124bdb712a941f79ac9edcba79b1/2025-04/6de869430891c2b786bd8401f5a3711.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        淘寶熱銷「對等關稅戰參戰」紀念杯。淘寶截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拼多多熱銷「對等關稅戰參戰」紀念杯。拼多多截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/49921474536595599422efb89d04898b/2025-04/06a2973d70044